            <div class="swiper-container slider-gallery js-gallery">
              <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                <div class="swiper-slide slider-item">
                  <div class="slider-gallery-img" style="background-image:url(<%- mix('/assets/images/granroom/granroom-banner.jpg') -%>)"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="swiper-slide slider-item">
                  <div class="slider-gallery-img" style="background-image:url(<%- mix('/assets/images/granroom/granroom-banner2.jpg') -%>)"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="swiper-container slider-gallery-thumb js-gallery-thumb">
              <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                <div class="swiper-slide slider-item">
                  <div class="slider-gallery-thumb-img" style="background-image:url(<%- mix('/assets/images/granroom/granroom-banner.jpg') -%>)"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="swiper-slide slider-item">
                  <div class="slider-gallery-thumb-img" style="background-image:url(<%- mix('/assets/images/granroom/granroom-banner2.jpg') -%>)"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="subpage-desc">
            <h3><b></b>あらびき那須三元豚とほうれん草のキッシュ</b></h3>
            通常の2倍ある広々とした部屋には幅4mのワイドベッドをはじめロッキングチェア、ハンモックが設けられ、心地よい木の香りに包まれながら森の中のようにリラックスしてお過ごしいただけます。
          </p>

        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="l-section point-item">
        <div class="l-container">
          <div class="l-section-title u-show-pc">
            <%- include('/partials/heading', {
              modifier: 'heading-forest heading-forest-craft',
              text: 'Point',
              alt: 'Point',
              subtextvg: 'craft-recommendation-title',
              altSubtext: '',
            }) %>
